# Modern UI & Packaging (The 2026 Standard)

Transform the Persona Agent system from a CLI-based tool into a premium, interactive Web Application with a standalone executable.

## User Experience Strategy: "Visual Sovereignty"

- **Aesthetics**: Dark mode, glassmorphism (frosted glass), high-contrast accent colors (vibrant cyan/purple), and smooth micro-animations.
- **Interactivity**: Real-time health gauge, interactive node map (entropy map), and a dynamic battle plan dashboard.
- **Portability**: Single `.exe` (Windows) that launches both the backend and the browser-based UI.

## Proposed Changes

### [Frontend - Web Dashboard]

#### [NEW] `src_ui/` (React + Vite + Vanilla CSS)
- **Dashboard**: High-level vitals (Health Score, Stability, Complexity).
- **System Map**: Visual representation of the project structure using canvas or SVG.
- **Report Viewer**: Beautifully rendered markdown reports with interactive toggles.

### [Backend - API Layer]

#### [NEW] `src_local/core/api.py` (FastAPI)
- Expose endpoints for [Orchestrator](file:///c:/Users/joaovitormagdaleno/Documents/GitHub/Personas_Agentes/src_local/core/orchestrator.py#13-136) findings, health data, and map metadata.
- Serve the static UI files in production mode.

### [Packaging - Standalone Executable]

#### [NEW] `scripts/build_exe.py`
- Configuration for `PyInstaller`.
- Hooks to bundle Python dependencies and the build folder of the React app.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Verify the UI opens automatically upon running the executable.
- Test responsiveness on different screen sizes.
- Confirm real-time updates when a file is manually edited.
